headline: Tesla nears record high close, Lennar & Steve Madden analyst calls
summary: As part of today's Market Minute, Yahoo Finance Senior Reporter Allie Canal examines some of the top trading day stories, including Tesla's (TSLA) trading highs, Raymond James downgrading Lennar (LEN), and Piper Sandler analysts upgrading Steven Madden (SHOO). headline: Sun Belt housing markets are so weak that homebuilder Lennar’s average home price is down 22%
summary: Lennar spent an average of 14.3% of its final sales price on incentives in Q3 2025. That’s its highest incentive rate since 2009.

headline: Lennar turnaround delayed on land costs, margin pressure, Raymond James says
summary: Investing.com -- Raymond James downgraded Lennar Corp to Underperform from Market Perform, saying the U.S. homebuilder faces a longer path to restoring margins and returns as higher-cost land, elevated incentives and overheads weigh on profitability.
